    "body": "Maybe i complicate it unnecessary.\r\nI will just pass to widgets as \"attributeName:\" variable with string. But variable is changed before algolia starts.\r\nThe problem is if I pass string \"price\" everything works. But if i pass string \"price_gb\" widgets doesn't starts. \r\nMy records looks like that:\r\n{\r\n  \"name\": \"Any name\",\r\n  \"price\": 45,\r\n  \"price_gb\": 49,\r\n  (...)\r\n}\r\nBoth are numerical, every record has the same fileds. Have I to do something with index? \r\n\r\nEDIT\r\nOk i solved it. Backend dev is on holidays and i don't know about \"Attributes for faceting\" option. After I add that field it works correctly.",
